<define-tag pagetitle>Debian Project Adopts a Constitution</define-tag>
<define-tag release_date>23 Nov 1998</define-tag>
#use wml::debian::news

<P>It's official.  The Debian has adopted a <A HREF="/devel/constitution">
constitution</A>.  The vote was virtually unanimous with 86 valid votes.

<P>The highlights of the constitution include the creation of the Technical
Committee, the Project Leader postion, the Project Secretary position, Leader
Delegate positions and a voting proceedure.

